Package logic.MapEntities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Door
    A door that can be opened by interacting with the map, or with itself.
    Empty
    The void in the map
    GenericMapEntity
    All entities in the map descent from this one.
    Hero
    The Hero, the figure controlled by the player, must go through all the levels in order to win the game.
    Key
    Keys spawn in some levels and are used to unlock the door to the next level.
    Lever
    Levers spawn in some levels and are use to immediately open a gateway door.
    Ogre
    The Ogre is a relentless foe that will swing its club and kill the Hero on contact.
    OgreClub
    The Ogre's club is a dangerous tool used to kill the hero.
    PickableClub
    Represents a club that the hero can pick, which will be used to stun nearby ogres.
    Wall
    The walls delimit the movable area and create impenetrable barriers.
